OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,6,Fbright spells. Turning cloudier
OL,7,Fthrough the middle of the day before
OL,8,Fbecoming clearer again towards
OL,9,Fevening. Largely dry with just the odd
OL,10,Fspot of rain, mainly west. Breezy at
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBecoming mostly dry and clear
OL,14,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,15,Fchance of the odd shower in the west.
OL,16,FOccasionally blustery southwest winds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FIt will be largely dry with
OL,19,Fbright or sunny spells in the morning.
OL,20,FChance of the odd shower developing in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon. Cooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
